{
  "stem": "26465.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And they took me in the-- this-- they came on a motorcycle, you know, in the car, a sidecar in the motorcycle, you know the sidecar.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And they were driving me, which is a very strange thing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I-- to this day, I don't know what happened.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They were riding with me to a forest.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I noticed now instead of going the regular highway to-- leading to Augsburg.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They were taking me to the forest.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was sure they were going to take advantage of me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were going to shoot me, or destroy me anyway.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was prepared already for my last day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And as they came into the forest, they tied me down to the tree.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they started all kinds of silly jumping around and thumping and showing off and diving, showing off, taking off their pants and so on.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And at a certain moment some old-- some guy, some old probably farmer-- I don't know where he came from and what he was for-- came to that.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And seeing it, he called him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they looked around to him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I don't know what happened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were so fast.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were so fast in untying me and putting me back into that-- that motorcycle.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they drove me at full speed to Augsburg.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I believe that was-- if you believe in angels-- that was an angel.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't think there was a-- and when I came there, and I was praying so much, thanking God that I came fine and safe out a it, was so relieved.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Oh my God, I know it doesn't matter maybe.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I will probably be punished in some small way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But that time, at least, I know where I am put and away from those henchmen.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
